---
title: Creamy Indian Chicken Curry with Baby Broccoli & Rice
description: This easy peasy chicken curry will be dished out and on the table in 25 minutes! The creamy base is flavoured with our mild curry
paste, enriching it with warm flavours and a golden hue. Pile it onto fluffy rice and dig in!
